{"tid":2272673,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"被指有角色衝突　游乃強無回應港台編導被捕案件問題","createTime":"2020-11-05T08:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T08:10:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02c73586a0f69c1688579244c8651f812c481e1f","tid":2272673,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"有份製作《鏗鏘集：7.21誰主真相 》的港台編導蔡玉玲前日被捕，警方指她涉嫌透過運輸署車牌查冊取得車主資料，用於不符合聲明所指的用途。新界北總區刑事部警司游乃強出席一個警方記者會時，沒有回應相關問題。<br />\n<br />\n有意見認為，在7.21事件中，游乃強是時任元朗助理指揮官，現時蔡玉玲案件由新界北重案組處理，有角色衝突問題。<br />\n<br />\n新界北總區下午舉行記者會，交代反三合會行動詳情，游乃強都有出席。游乃強被問到有關問題時，主持說記者會談及反三合會行動，想知道其他資料要向新聞室查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558518-20201105.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558518-20201105.htm&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4CPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=985a7195\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558518-20201105.htm&h=5d513979\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558518-20201105.htm</a>"},{"pid":"29b972de035dcc1c42062859efc8c78acb9d578f","tid":2272673,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345960f11523110263e474e77b45fd0d4ed889b8","tid":2272673,"uid":92125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"原來又係游乃強哩隻狗查"},{"pid":"fe6b71d38e923ab389035ff7c6301b7d2ff28bd3","tid":2272673,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T08:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/